        <title>Used Functions</title>
        <para>
            qr decomposition is based  the Lapack routines DGEQRF, DGEQPF,
            DORGQR for the real matrices and  ZGEQRF, ZGEQPF, ZORGQR for the
            complex case.
        </para>
